mcut-swift
==========

This package wraps and redistributes mcut, a mesh cutting / boolean library by
CutDigital Enterprise.

  mcut — https://github.com/cutdigital/mcut
  Copyright (c) CutDigital Enterprise
  Licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public License, Version 3 (LGPL-3.0).

The mcut binary is distributed here as a prebuilt, dynamically linked
xcframework (Cmcut.xcframework), produced unmodified from the upstream source
pinned at tag v1.3.0. The corresponding source is available from the URL above
at that tag.

As required by the LGPL, the library is shipped as a dynamic, replaceable
framework. See LICENSE (LGPL-3.0) and COPYING (GPL-3.0, incorporated by the
LGPL) for the full license texts, and README.md for what this means for your
app and how to obtain a commercial license for mcut from CutDigital.
